# 统一行尾,避免 Windows autocrlf 把脚本/配置写成 CRLF 后在 Linux 容器里崩
# (踩过:CRLF 让容器内 shell 脚本报 `bash\r: no such file`)
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml  text eol=lf
*.likec4 text eol=lf
*.conf text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf

# 二进制别动
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
